The paper deals with improving the segmentation of human brain areas using neural networks, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of self-supervised learning is a key aspect of the paper, which is a popular topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also involves natural language processing (cs.CL) to some extent, as it discusses the use of expert annotations for training.
